 |CKBRemort Boons
|WKO~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 |YKOBoons are permanent bonuses bought with boon points. You earn
 one boon point each time you remort (see |YKBhelp remort|YKO). Boons
 survive death, rebirth, and every remort that follows: once a
 boon is part of your soul, it is never lost.

 |MKBChoosing boons:
  |YKB remort boons          |YKOList all boons, your ranks, and costs
  |YKB remort boon <name>    |YKOSee the details of one boon
  |YKB remort choose <name>  |YKOSpend a point on a rank of a boon
  |YKB marks                 |YKOReview the boons on your soul

 |YKOEach boon can be taken multiple times, up to its maximum rank.
 Choices are permanent, so weigh them carefully.

 |MKBThe boons:
  |YKOBoon of Vitality    +2% maximum hit points per rank
  Boon of Spirit      +2% maximum spell points per rank
  Boon of Might       +2 strength per rank
  Boon of Grace       +2 dexterity per rank
  Boon of Endurance   +2 constitution per rank
  Boon of Intellect   +2 intelligence per rank
  Boon of Insight     +2 wisdom per rank
  Boon of Presence    +2 charisma per rank
  Soul Memory         +5% experience gained per rank

 |YKOSouls tempered by many lives unlock greater boons:

  |YKOMythic Vitality     +5% maximum hit points per rank
                      (requires remort 5, costs 2 points)
  Mythic Spirit       +5% maximum spell points per rank
                      (requires remort 5, costs 2 points)

 |YKOStat boons stack on top of your trained stats and are not
 limited by the normal stat caps. More boons will be added over
 time, including some that only open at higher remort levels.

 |YKOSee also: |YKBhelp remort|YKO.
